<h2 id="about">About</h2>
<p1>WELCOME TO HOMESPUN LATHER!</p1><br>
  <p2>At Homespun Lather, I create cold process soaps in small batches that contain natural ingredients you can feel confident putting on your skin. I believe the things you put on your body are just as important as the things you put in your body.

My soaps do not contain artificial fragrances, colorants, preservatives, or other fillers. In fact, many of the ingredients in my soaps are things I would feel confident feeding my family (before they become soap, of course).</p2>
